Package org.dataflowanalysis.pcm.extension.nodecharacteristics.nodecharacteristics

Interface NodeCharacteristicsPackage

All Superinterfaces:
EModelElement, ENamedElement, EObject, EPackage, Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
NodeCharacteristicsPackageImpl
public interface NodeCharacteristicsPackage extends EPackage
The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
See Also:
  • NodeCharacteristicsFactory
